&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">1️⃣Hint 1: Have you checked the contents of the /root folder?
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">2️⃣Hint 2: Find a way to add more instruction to ls
